Haa... Haa...
...How did it go!?

Yeah, we were pretty on point──...
I mean, to put it modestly, it was amazing...!?

Well, there weren't any noticeable mistakes
so it might have gone well.

Y-yeah...
It felt like we were all... as one...

That's right... But
if I may interrupt──...

Look... you've been tense this whole time. The performance
is approaching, so you need to relax where you can.

Ah... um...
...Then, Yuika-chan...!

Huh? What's up~?
Are you asking Kiriko for a shoulder massage?

If Yuika-chan... doesn't mind...
I'll share some happiness...!

Of course it's fine!
Then, the next target is Kogane!

Eh!? ...Wow, Yuika, you're good~
That feels great~

Hehe, then...
The next sharing is for Mamimi!

Eh...?
I-I'd rather not be involved...
Wow, it's like the fatigue from earlier was just a lie!

Hehe...
Being with everyone... makes me happy...

Yeah, I feel the same way.
With these five, I feel like we can go anywhere──...

Such a romantic~
...Well, it doesn't seem like it'll be boring, right?
Mamimi, it won't be boring at all!

From here on...
our story begins from our debut live...!
